abstract: "Clawpack is a comprehensive legal reference system containing modular legal knowledge structures across 50+ practice areas with 8,000+ verified URLs to authoritative sources. LawClaw, a component of Clawpack, provides structured legal references for AI agents, legal research, academic study, and professional practice."
